* Iron Raptor shook Quakes hand and simply let go, not failing to see both 
Kluster and Prowl race from the room to help defend the Cybertronian Fire.
But she listened to all that quake said and actually found it a bit 
interesting, but then also think that a few other Maximals might have a few 
of the same trates.
But it was fairly obviouse that this bot would be a welcomed fighter on the 
field, a perfect person to set on defenses on the Ark when she sent the 
repair group out.
Iron Raptor looked quake over once more.*

" It seems like I could put your tallents to work, Quake. Um, how would you 
like to help with defenses on the Ark?"
